nodes.text: Docking Bay D-768 was a docking bay situated within Fleet Support's Air Station on the Mid Rim planet Ord Mantell. In use by the Galactic Republic's Grand Army in 22 BBY, Docking Bay D-768 housed a Nar Shaddaa agri-utility crop sprayer that transported the clone commandos of Omega Squad to the nearby world of Qiilura on a mission to locate and neutralize Separatist scientist Ovolot Qail Uthan in order to suspend her progress on the clone-killing nanovirus FG36.
Docking Bay D-768 appeared in the 2004 novel Republic Commando: Hard Contact by Karen Traviss.
